Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN END
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
roty -gs_rot_ver rotx gs_rot_hor addx 1.6755
!!---------!! !! Chassis !! !!---------!! call "TC_Chassis" parameters gs_chassis_mat=gs_carbody_mat
!!--------!! !! Wheels !! !!--------!!
dist_x=0.9354+1.6755 dist_y=0.688*2
addx -1.6755 for j=1 to 2 addy dist_y/2 for i=1 to 2 call "TC_Wheel" parameters a=0.615,b=0.192,zzyzx=0.615,angle=0,gs_wheel_mat=gs_wheel_mat muly -1 addy dist_y next i del 5 addx dist_x next j del 3
!!-------!! !! Doors !! !!-------!! for i=1 to 2 call "TC_FrontDoor" parameters gs_frame_mat=gs_frame_mat,gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_mirror_mat=gs_mirror_mat,gs_glass_mat=gs_glass_mat call "TC_BackDoor" parameters gs_frame_mat=gs_frame_mat,gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_glass_mat=gs_glass_mat muly -1 next i del 2
!!---------!! !! Bumpers !! !!---------!! call "TC_FrontBumper" parameters gs_bumper_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_numplate_mat=gs_access_mat,gs_airgrill_mat=gs_access_mat call "TC_RearBumper" parameters gs_bumper_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_access_mat=gs_access_mat
!!---------!! !! CarSide !! !!---------!! for i=1 to 2 call "TC_CarSide" parameters gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_access_mat=gs_access_mat muly -1 next i del 2
!!--------!! !! CarTop !! !!--------!! call "TC_CarTop" parameters gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_access_mat=gs_access_mat,gs_frame_mat=gs_frame_mat,gs_glass_mat=gs_glass_mat
!!----------------!! !! Bonnet & Trunk !! !!----------------!! call "TC_Bonnet" parameters gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_access_mat=gs_access_mat,gs_grill_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_mark_mat=gs_mark_mat call "TC_Trunk" parameters gs_carbody_mat=gs_carbody_mat,gs_mark_mat=gs_mark_mat
!!-------!! !! Lamps !! !!-------!! for i=1 to 2 call "TC_FrontLamp" parameters gs_lamp_mat=gs_lamp_mat,gs_lampin_mat=gs_lampin_mat call "TC_RearLamp" parameters gs_blamp_mat=gs_blamp_mat muly -1 next i del 2
!!----------!! !! Interior !! !!----------!! If interior Then for i=1 to 2 call "TC_Interior" parameters gs_int_mat1=gs_int_mat1,gs_int_mat2=gs_int_mat2 muly -1 next i del 2 If wheel Then muly -1 call "TC_Dashboard" parameters gs_dashb_mat=gs_int_mat1 If wheel Then del 1 EndIf
del 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_rot_ver" range[-45,45] values "gs_rot_hor" range[-30,30]
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
Symbol.Comment: Автомобиль с дополнительным правым рулем и внутренним дисплеем.
